quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  36,41,"Ne ni eshimanyisio khubo mbu efwe khwachinga olwibulo lwabu musafina yitsule."
  36,42,"Ne nikhubalonjela okhurula khufwani eyo ebiabaninangakhwo."
  36,43,"Ne nikhwenya, nikhubasishia mumatsi, ne abulaho ubakhoonya nohomba shibahabinwa tawe."
  36,44,"Halali tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwifwe, nende omwikhoyo kwebise bititi."
  36,45,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu: “Mwilinde ehale nende kali imbeli wenyu nende kali inyuma wenyu, khomunyoole okhubeelwa tsimbabaasi.”"
  36,46,"Ne sishiboolelanga eshimanyisio shiosishiosi mubimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, halali shibabukulangamwo oluchendo tawe."
  36,47,"Ne nibaboolelwa mbu: “Hane khubilia bia Nyasaye abakabile", Abakhayi baboolelenga Abasuubili mbu: “Koo, khulisie balia ba Nyasaye niyenya nabalisia? Toto enywe muli mubukori bwa habulafu.”"
  36,48,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Kamukhulakanga kano kalirulila lina, nimuli toto abahabwene?”"
  36,49,"Shibalindanga halali oluyoka lulala butswa lulibabukula nabo nibali mukhusolana."
  36,50,"Mana shibalinyoola okhulaamila nohomba shibalikalukha khubandu babu tawe."
  36,51,"Na olwa olwika lulifurwamwo, balirula mubilindwa nibelushila ewa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  36,52,"Baliboola mbu: “Abayie! Wina ukhulamusiyie okhurula wakhubeele nikhukonele. Kano niko aka Omunji wetsimbabaasi yalaka, ne Abarumwa nibaboola katoto.”"
  36,53,"Ne shiluliba halali oluyoka lulala butswa, ne lola, boosi balikhung’asibwa imbeli wefu."
  36,54,"Mana olwa lelo abulaho yesiyesi ulikholelwa amabii kosikosi, ne shimulirungwa halali kalia kamwakholanga."